productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Germaine has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks red.
This Unbranded works too well. It buoyantly improves my football by a lot.
The box this comes in is 5 foot by 6 inch and weights 17 pound!!!
i use it occasionally when i'm in my outhouse.
heard about this on Kansas City jazz radio, decided to give it a try.
